seBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20240813134012-4rj4sqg.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"}]}]},{"ID":"20240813134014-sbl6oin","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240813134014-sbl6oin","updated":"20240813134014"}},{"ID":"20240813134015-6vvopxi","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20240813134015-6vvopxi","updated":"20240813134042"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20240813134017-ucnm7qo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240813134017-ucnm7qo","updated":"20240813134042"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"5.设置名称"}]},{"ID":"20240813134042-ao68zuc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240813134042-ao68zuc","updated":"20240813134042"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20240813134042-zfh5bsb.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"}]}]},{"ID":"20240813134108-10sqqth","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240813134108-10sqqth","updated":"20240813134108"}},{"ID":"20240813134109-w5a5mle","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20240813134109-w5a5mle","updated":"20240813134140"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20240813134109-geaki3k","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240813134109-geaki3k","updated":"20240813134137"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"6.先运行一下代码（不需要写任何东西），选择gpu加速"}]},{"ID":"20240813134140-asx2mab","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240813134140-asx2mab","updated":"20240813134140"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20240813134140-142jg5o.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"}]}]},{"ID":"20240813134142-en5zqrw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240813134142-en5zqrw","updated":"20240813134142"}},{"ID":"20240813134143-8wrdlhg","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20240813134143-8wrdlhg","updated":"20240813134217"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20240813134143-ccv9jx2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240813134143-ccv9jx2","updated":"20240813134155"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"7.在 执行代码程序-\u003e更改运行时类型-\u003eGPU 这样才能够使用GPU资源来进行我们的深度学习。\n在换成GPU资源以后，你可以用以下代码测试你是否真正连接上了GPU资源："}]},{"ID":"20240813134216-m6p908q","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240813134216-m6p908q","updated":"20240813134217"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"若输出为"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"Found GPU at: /device:GPU:0"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​则证明你连接成功。"}]},{"ID":"20240813134157-ulwuobq","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20240813134157-ulwuobq","updated":"20240813134209"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"cHl0aG9u"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"import tensorflow as tf\ndevice_name = tf.test.gpu_device_name()\nif device_name != '/device:GPU:0':\n raise SystemError('GPU device not found')\nprint('Found GPU at: {}'.format(device_name))\n\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]}]},{"ID":"20240813134203-08s6969","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240813134203-08s6969","updated":"20240813134203"}},{"ID":"20240813134234-u0el2kj","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20240813134234-u0el2kj","updated":"20240813134326"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20240813134236-omt77ss","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240813134236-omt77ss","updated":"20240813134244"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"8.挂载谷歌云盘"}]},{"ID":"20240813134311-4ka02l8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240813134311-4ka02l8","updated":"20240813134326"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"ls '/content/gdrive/My Drive/colabData/captured_images'"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​使用这个命令可查看是否挂载成功"}]},{"ID":"20240813134244-b0y63a1","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20240813134244-b0y63a1","updated":"20240813134251"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"cHl0aG9u"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"from google.colab import drive\ndrive.mount('/content/gdrive')\n\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]}]},{"ID":"20240813134252-ilhlix3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240813134252-ilhlix3","updated":"20240813134252"}},{"ID":"20240813134328-468pbfl","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20240813134328-468pbfl","updated":"20240813134351"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20240813134329-q8xfkrx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240813134329-q8xfkrx","updated":"20240813134351"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"9.查看gpu性能"}]},{"ID":"20240813134346-yo0glrs","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20240813134346-yo0glrs","updated":"20240813134346"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"cHl0aG9u"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"!nvidia-smi\n\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]}]},{"ID":"20240813134354-ugcrobb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240813134354-ugcrobb","updated":"20240813134354"}},{"ID":"20240813134354-j2q20zc","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20240813134354-j2q20zc","updated":"20240813134419"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20240813134355-53b3pmr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240813134355-53b3pmr","updated":"20240813134415"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"10.安装yolov5"}]},{"ID":"20240813134416-igqs7j6","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20240813134416-igqs7j6","updated":"20240813134419"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"cHl0aG9u"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"!git clone https://github.com/ultralytics/yolov5\n%cd yolov5\n!pip install -U -r requirements.txt\n\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]}]},{"ID":"20240813134421-z0g9ve2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240813134421-z0g9ve2","updated":"20240813134421"}},{"ID":"20240813134531-arxiplo","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20240813134531-arxiplo","updated":"20240813134637"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20240813134531-v3zyqvy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240813134531-v3zyqvy","updated":"20240813134546"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"11.（选做）"}]},{"ID":"20240813134547-e5yglct","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240813134547-e5yglct","updated":"20240813134552"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"自动打标签"}]},{"ID":"20240813134556-ldz1g4s","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240813134556-ldz1g4s","updated":"20240813134557"}},{"ID":"20240813134621-r4wd5yn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240813134621-r4wd5yn","updated":"20240813134637"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"可以指定需要的类别 ID"}]},{"ID":"20240813134621-s141nx6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240813134621-s141nx6","updated":"20240813134631"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"target_class_id = 0"}]},{"ID":"20240813134558-x8achwc","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20240813134558-x8achwc","updated":"20240813134631"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"cHl0aG9u"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"import cv2\nimport torch\nimport os\n\n# 加载预训练的YOLOv5模型\nmodel = torch.hub.load('ultralytics/yolov5', 'yolov5s')\n\n# 设置图像目录和保存标注的目录\nimage_dir = '/content/gdrive/My Drive/colabData/captured_images'\nlabel_dir = '/content/gdrive/My Drive/colabData/labelImg'\n\nif not os.path.exists(label_dir):\n    os.makedirs(label_dir)\n\n# 获取图像列表\nimage_files = [f for f in os.listdir(image_dir) if f.endswith(('.png', '.jpg', '.jpeg'))]\n\n# 指定需要的类别 ID\ntarget_class_id = 0\n\n# 处理每个图像\nfor image_file in image_files:\n    image_path = os.path.join(image_dir, image_file)\n    img = cv2.imread(image_path)\n    height, width, _ = img.shape\n\n    # 使用模型进行推理\n    results = model(img)\n\n    # 提取检测结果并转换为YOLO格式\n    yolo_annotations = []\n    for result in results.xyxy[0]:\n        xmin, ymin, xmax, ymax, conf, cls = result\n        label_id = int(cls)\n\n        # 只处理指定类别\n        if label_id == target_class_id:\n            # 归一化坐标 (x_center, y_center, width, height)\n            x_center = (xmin + xmax) / 2.0 / width\n            y_center = (ymin + ymax) / 2.0 / height\n            bbox_width = (xmax - xmin) / width\n            bbox_height = (ymax - ymin) / height\n\n            # YOLO格式：\u003cclass_id\u003e \u003cx_center\u003e \u003cy_center\u003e \u003cwidth\u003e \u003cheight\u003e\n            yolo_annotation = f\"{label_id} {x_center:.6f} {y_center:.6f} {bbox_width:.6f} {bbox_height:.6f}\"\n            yolo_annotations.append(yolo_annotation)\n\n    # 保存YOLO格式的标注文件\n    txt_filename = os.path.splitext(image_file)[0] + '.txt'\n    txt_path = os.path.join(label_dir, txt_filename)\n    with open(txt_path, 'w') as f:\n        f.write(\"\\n\".join(yolo_annotations))\n\n    print(f\"Saved annotation for {image_file} as {txt_filename}\")\n\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]}]},{"ID":"20240813134641-3suycao","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240813134641-3suycao","updated":"20240813134641"}},{"ID":"20240813134642-rkjr5id","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20240813134642-rkjr5id","updated":"20240813134825"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20240813134645-le02p0w","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240813134645-le02p0w","updated":"20240813134713"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"12.将图片和训练集复制到images的train和val"}]},{"ID":"20240813134737-a7xms3v","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20240813134737-a7xms3v","updated":"20240813134741"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"cHl0aG9u"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"import shutil\n\n# 源文件夹路径\nsource_folder = '/content/gdrive/My Drive/colabData/captured_val'\n# 目标文件夹路径\ndestination_folder = '/content/gdrive/My Drive/colabData/images/val'\n\n# 复制文件夹及其所有内容，允许目标文件夹已存在\nshutil.copytree(source_folder, destination_folder, dirs_exist_ok=True)\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20240813134738-gcbyvm2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240813134738-gcbyvm2","updated":"20240813134825"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"全部复制完后再将整个images文件夹复制一遍为labels（这是因为实际训练的时候总是会跑到这个文件夹里去找文件）"}]},{"ID":"20240813134713-6yzc6o3","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20240813134713-6yzc6o3","updated":"20240813134715"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"cHl0aG9u"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"import shutil\n\n# 源文件夹路径\nsource_folder = '/content/gdrive/My Drive/colabData/labels'\n# 目标文件夹路径\ndestination_folder = '/content/gdrive/My Drive/colabData/images'\n\n# 复制文件夹及其所有内容，允许目标文件夹已存在\nshutil.copytree(source_folder, destination_folder, dirs_exist_ok=True)\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]}]},{"ID":"20240813134717-irj0iga","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240813134717-irj0iga","updated":"20240813134717"}},{"ID":"20240813134838-s79n03m","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20240813134838-s79n03m","updated":"20240813134921"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20240813134839-a8c2e2a","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240813134839-a8c2e2a","updated":"20240813134910"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"13.在yolov5文件夹下创建data.yaml文件"}]},{"ID":"20240813134911-5x59sdh","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20240813134911-5x59sdh","updated":"20240813134921"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"cHl0aG9u"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"train: \"/content/gdrive/My Drive/colabData/images/train\"\nval: \"/content/gdrive/My Drive/colabData/images/val\"\n\n\nnc: 1  # 你使用的类别数量\nnames: ['0']  # 类别名称列表\n\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]}]},{"ID":"20240813134924-mnsymv8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240813134924-mnsymv8","updated":"20240813134924"}},{"ID":"20240813134925-bbict21","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20240813134925-bbict21","updated":"20240813135022"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20240813134926-o00u1ku","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240813134926-o00u1ku","updated":"20240813134935"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"14.进行训练"}]},{"ID":"20240813134935-hq4nlef","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20240813134935-hq4nlef","updated":"20240813135022"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"cHl0aG9u"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"!python train.py --img 640 --batch 16 --epochs 50 --data /content/yolov5/data.yaml --weights yolov5s.pt\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]}]},{"ID":"20240813135025-ct1c521","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240813135025-ct1c521"}}]}